tr.edu.bilkent.cs.patoh
Class PartitioningParameters

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.jna.Structure
      tr.edu.bilkent.cs.patoh.PartitioningParameters

public class PartitioningParameters
extends com.sun.jna.Structure

Java equivalent of PaToH_Parameters, and simply extending this class (probably) won't work -- try to use spare fields (allargs, inputfilename, etc.) instead.

After creating a PartitioningParameters instance, before passing it to any parititoning functions, you must invoke initialize method of the instance.
